With InDesign CS6 and a Creative Cloud subscription it has gotten a whole lot easier to create an unlimited number of applications for the iPad. Join Terry White worldwide Creative Suite Design Evangelist for Adobe Systems as he takes you through every step in the process for creating an iPad app from scratch up to submitting it for approval in the App Store. Youll learn what software is required to complete each phase of the project how to create alternate versions for vertical and horizontal orientations how to add various forms of interactivity and how to build the final app itself.
